Firstly

Convert between the twelve forms of numeric, written and ordinal numbers:

From   To     Use                Status
--------------------------------------------
1      one    NumToOrdinal()     Implemented
1      1st    NumToOrd()         Implemented
1      first  NumToNumber()      Implemented
one    1      NumberToNum()      Coming
one    1st    NumberToOrd()      Coming
one    first  NumberToOrdinal()  Implemented
1st    1      OrdToNum()         Implemented
1st    one    OrdToNumber()      Implemented
1st    first  OrdToOrdinal()     Implemented
first  1      OrdinalToNum()     Coming
first  one    OrdinalToNumber()  Coming
first  1st    OrdinalToOrd()     Coming

Each function accepts an optional second parameter to control the
capitalisation of the return value (where appropriate):

Value  Means
-----------------------------
0      all lower case
1      Leading capital letter
2      Title Case
3      ALL CAPS

Requires Salman Halim's NumberToEnglish plugin:
http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2561

